@echo off\nREM Terraform Deployment Script for Windows\nREM Purpose: Initialize, validate, plan, and apply Terraform configuration\n\nsetlocal enabledelayedexpansion\n\necho ================================================\necho   Terraform Infrastructure Deployment\necho ================================================\necho.\n\nREM Get script directory\nset \"TF_DIR=%~dp0..\\terraform\"\ncd /d \"%TF_DIR%\"\n\necho Working directory: %TF_DIR%\necho.\n\nREM Check prerequisites\necho [INFO] Checking prerequisites...\n\nwhere terraform >nul 2>nul\nif %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 (\n    echo [ERROR] terraform not found. Please install Terraform.\n    exit /b 1\n)\n\nwhere kubectl >nul 2>nul\nif %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 (\n    echo [ERROR] kubectl not found. Please install kubectl.\n    exit /b 1\n)\n\nkubectl cluster-info >nul 2>nul\nif %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 (\n    echo [ERROR] Cannot connect to Kubernetes cluster.\n    exit /b 1\n)\n\necho [INFO] Prerequisites met\necho.\n\nREM Terraform init\necho [INFO] Initializing Terraform...\nterraform init\nif %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 (\n    echo [ERROR] Terraform init failed\n    exit /b 1\n)\necho [INFO] Terraform initialized\necho.\n\nREM Terraform validate\necho [INFO] Validating Terraform configuration...\nterraform validate\nif %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 (\n    echo [ERROR] Configuration invalid\n    exit /b 1\n)\necho [INFO] Configuration valid\necho.\n\nREM Check for terraform.tfvars\nif not exist \"terraform.tfvars\" (\n    echo [WARN] terraform.tfvars not found\n    echo [INFO] Creating from example...\n    copy terraform.tfvars.example terraform.tfvars\n    echo [WARN] Please update terraform.tfvars with your values\n)\n\nREM Terraform plan\necho [INFO] Planning infrastructure changes...\nterraform plan -out=tfplan\necho.\n\nREM Ask for confirmation\nset /p confirm=\"Do you want to apply these changes? (yes/no): \"\necho.\nif /i not \"%confirm%\"==\"yes\" (\n    echo [INFO] Deployment cancelled\n    exit /b 0\n)\n\nREM Terraform apply\necho [INFO] Applying infrastructure changes...\nterraform apply -auto-approve tfplan\nif %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 (\n    echo [ERROR] Terraform apply failed\n    exit /b 1\n)\necho [INFO] Infrastructure deployed\necho.\n\nREM Display outputs\necho [INFO] Terraform Outputs:\nterraform output -json\necho.\n\necho ================================================\necho   Terraform Deployment Complete\necho ================================================\necho.\npause\n"